Entry.EnglishText: ...I have to defeat Yuris... No matter what...!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Annie>、もうちっと肩の力抜けよ。 そんな気負うなって。
Entry.EnglishText: <Annie>, you need to take it easy. Don't let yourself get all worked up.

Entry.JapaneseText: はい……でも、わたし、この中でも一番 力が弱いし、がんばらなくちゃって……
Entry.EnglishText: I know... But, I'm the weakest among us, so I need to do my best...

Entry.JapaneseText: お前は充分強いぜ！ おれが五つ星を保証してやる！ 言っとくけど、気休めなんかじゃないからな。
Entry.EnglishText: You're strong enough as is! I give you a five star rating! I'm not just saying that to make you feel better, either.

Entry.JapaneseText: ありがとうございます。 わたし、がんばります……！
Entry.EnglishText: Thank you very much. I'm going to do my best!

Entry.JapaneseText: だから肩の力抜けって。将来、医者になるんだろ？ 医者がそんなんじゃ、患者がブルっちまうぜ！
Entry.EnglishText: Just take it easy. You're going to be a doctor in the future, right? You woudn't want to intimidate your patients!
Entry.Notes: Lit. With Doctor like that, patients becoem scared
